<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="J%20Biomed%20Inform"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>The National Institutes of Health's Biomedical Translational Research Information System (BTRIS): Design, Contents, Functionality and Experience to Date</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Cimino%20JJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">James J Cimino</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">James J Cimino</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Laboratory for Informatics Development, NIH Clinical Center, Bethesda, MD</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Cimino%20JJ"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">James J Cimino</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ayres%20EJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Elaine J Ayres</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
