<sup>a</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Remennik%20L"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Lyubov Remennik</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Lyubov Remennik</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
